reviewText: Is is what I was looking for, I like it very much. Fast service.looking for more , want to get all tneir shows.

Sharon, Lois & Bram yet again produce an excellent video for kids! In this video, Sharon, Lois & Bram perfrom live in concert in Canada singing and dancing to great songs. A little dated and not at all "cheesy" like today's kids shows. They sing songs for every letter of the alphabet. I would recommend this video mainly for 4-8 year olds... but younger and older can still enjoy this video. This video is also released on DVD titled "Sharon, Lois & Bram's ABCs"....
